Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:10.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The Detective Boys head to a Kamen Yaiba show on the roof of Marutan Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:16.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\blur2}Not knowing that we would face an unbelievable case there afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:21.22,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Solving riddles with sharp powers of deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.22,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The starting points of love and cases always remain the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:26.92,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Detectives versus robbers in a closed department store!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.59,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.50,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.84,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
