Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We have you now, Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Send him to hell, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Yaiba, shall defend world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of those jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:40.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:43.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm in high school. So what\Nam I doing watching this drivel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't you like Yaiba, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:56.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it! Go, Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Talk about fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:14.25,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Thank you for shopping with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:20.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Thank you. We look forward to seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:28.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba! Yaiba! He fights for justice! Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:31.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba's autograph is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:43.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we took the picture with Yaiba,\NI seem to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the picture, Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:55.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to recall Genta saying that he was hungry when we took this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:02.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I bought a hot dog and thenâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's at that shop! I'm going to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:11.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the place is closed by now.\NI say leave it for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:14.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want! I'm going to go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:16.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:22.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. My deductive skills are to blame for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:31.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry! The security system\Nis going to activate in 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:38.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}. That door's going to lock\Nwhen the security system activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get it in less than 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:01.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! My treasure's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All thanks to Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s great detective skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:09.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this was nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:11.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We better hurry before the\Nsecurity system activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to the security guards'\Noffice inside the building
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and explain the situation,\NI'm sure they'll let us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:36.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Security Office! Floor B2!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:45.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamen Yaibâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The jewelry store's on the 6th floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:52.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And there are antiques in the\Nconvention hall on the 7th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the elevator ladyâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:58.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. We have until morning\Nto take whatever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gang of thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in big trouble if they find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll kill us! Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the elevator lady\Nand those other people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:11.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's stay hidden\Nand contact the police! OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:11.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! There's no dial tone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cord's been cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've all been cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use this phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. It doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:36.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The phones must be down\Nbecause of the security system!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So nobody's going to come to rescue us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:43.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat a ton of eel\Nlunches before I get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to give up just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Please notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It didn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:10.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The robbers will hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, it won't break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:23.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up! The windows here\Nare made of especially thick glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Security office! There's a weird sound\Ncoming from the 7th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:59.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Use the security cameras\Nto check out the 7th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pooped...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it was pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:07.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan! What about the window?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! You won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing strange that I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:26.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing strange?! Those were\Nsome pretty loud sounds we heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's take the loot and split!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Let's check it out just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, aren't there any exits around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, you little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make dinner right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:06.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've seen our faces! Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:08.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:20.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Security office! Do you read me?!\NTurn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say? I didn't copy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:24.66,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's a bunch of little brats in the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:32.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Where'd those lousy kids go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.94,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey! What's going on?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The other guys in the security\Noffice know we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They turned on the lights to catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:07.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad. Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:19.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} still hasn't come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know where that lousy kid is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:27.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta! Get out! Everyone out! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They almost had us trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:59.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Save that for after we get out of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:04.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I thought Conan was at the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:08.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he go with his friends\Nto see some kids' show?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pitch dark outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:13.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try calling the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my food, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:22.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to starve me to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.45,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:29.41,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is Marutan Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:33.12,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We are currently closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:38.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hurry! We need to get as far away\Nfrom them as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:45.43,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We will be open during our regular\Nhours tomorrow, from 10 AMâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:53.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}See? So what do you say you\Nmake me some dinner now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:55.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now who are you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:57.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Kojima household? This is Ran Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:58.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}â€”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:10.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here and hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:10.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:14.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:17.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there! This is the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have this department store surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your weapons down and release the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no police here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:49.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They used a bunch\Nof stupid mannequins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let 'em get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:59.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Yoshida residence?\NI'm Conan Edogawa'sâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:04.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0} hasn't come home yet either?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a call from Mitsuhiko-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s family too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:12.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:24.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, Genta! Do you want them to catch you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:27.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:46.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:09.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I just realized something strange,\Nbut I don't know what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan and his friends were kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is that they're taking\Ntheir sweet time coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:25.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be back soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:30.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's about some dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:38.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Cook me some food alreadyâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the investigation department?\NInspector Megure, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Works better than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:51.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:54.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real liability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:08.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you at such a late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:14.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any incidents at the moment\Nthat might involve the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:18.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is strange that none of\Nthem have returned home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could something have happened to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've put out a bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:26.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they'll turn up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:32.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now if you'll excuse me,\NI'm in the middle of an important case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:37.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've done all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All there is to do now is wait\Nfor any reports about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's goâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:56.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to do this at least once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:16:00.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us. We'll pay for this\Nif we make it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we even will make it out alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so down, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:11.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had plenty to eat now, so cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:15.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to take care of them\Nand get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:18.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Detective Boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:29.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it must be a pretty important case\Nif they're still at it this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:33.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}\Nand the others aren't important?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:42.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn that Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:46.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm missing my dinner thanks to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A gang of department store thieves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:56.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They sneak in after the stores close\Nand steal jewelry and electronics...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:17:00.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be the important\Ncase he was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Department store?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Commence counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:26.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now where are they hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:27.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:45.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't handle alcohol well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay! We can't let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:24.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:26.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fetch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:47.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:51.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Aha! Now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:03.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, elevator lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:11.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:14.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, we're in dangerâ€”\Nthere are some bad people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can drop the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's going on, elevator lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:26.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, the 5th member of the thief gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:34.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a 5th person who\Nactivated the escalator earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:37.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This person had been waiting\Nto catch all four of us at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:40.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the remaining people\Nin the security office,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:44.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you were the only one who knew\Nhow many of us there were.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:48.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You planned in advance to get inside\Nby getting a job as an elevator girl
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you could scout out the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:55.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:57.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent deductive work, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:02.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems you didn't know that\NI was actually the gang's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A pistol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair that you have a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:10.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}OK! I'll lure her onto the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The game's over, little boy! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:37.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Basketballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Annoying little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:48.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your pointless resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:57.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:19.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:41.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:45.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the thieves! Take them into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:49.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of silly kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:54.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:04.05,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi e no uso
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:24.28,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The following day, we were\Ngiven an award ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:26.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}for capturing the thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:28.05,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We didn't have to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:32.22,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}for any of the things we ate\Nor broke inside the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:33.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is that really alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:35.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chalk another one upâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
